Do not supplicate for help today; you will not be rescued by Us;
TQA2739,QA2739,TLQ01,'For when My revelations were read out to you, you turned back on your heels and fled'
TQA2740,QA2740,TLQ01,'Insolently, treating them like tales told at night.'
